---
openapi: "3.0.0"

  title: Ganymede Kernel Rest Protocol
  description: Ganymede Kernel Rest Protocol
  version: 2.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://localhost/
paths:
  /kernel/id:
    get:
      summary: Get Kernel UUID
      operationId: kernelId
      parameters: [ ]

          content:

              schema:
                type: UUID

              type: JsonNode
